WEBVTT

00:00.633 --> 00:04.103
♪

00:06.139 --> 00:07.106
Whoa, whoa, whoa ahhhhhh!

00:07.108 --> 00:08.073
[smashing glass]

00:08.075 --> 00:09.008
Agh!

00:12.045 --> 00:15.381
Well, we don't all
have magical horns.

00:15.383 --> 00:17.316
I've been meaning to
move these older books

00:17.318 --> 00:19.385
to my "reference"
section for a while.

00:19.387 --> 00:21.520
Gotta keep the new
books front and center!

00:21.522 --> 00:23.355
Thank you both for
your help.

00:23.357 --> 00:25.724
Are you kidding? After
all you've done for me?

00:25.726 --> 00:27.559
This is the least
I can do.

00:27.561 --> 00:30.062
Oh please, I haven't
done that much.

00:30.064 --> 00:33.332
Nah. You just taught me
the value of friendship.

00:33.334 --> 00:35.334
Not much at all.

00:35.336 --> 00:37.236
I may have offered
some guidance,

00:37.238 --> 00:40.039
but you are responsible
for the pony you've become.

00:40.041 --> 00:43.075
I'm proud to call you my
student AND my friend.

00:43.077 --> 00:45.277
Now, we just need to
get rid of these boxes.

00:45.279 --> 00:47.513
Spike, can you... Spike?

00:47.515 --> 00:49.081
What's that?

00:50.517 --> 00:52.317
Is it a bird?

00:52.319 --> 00:53.819
Is it a parasprite?

00:53.821 --> 00:56.688
It's... It's... INCOMING!!

00:56.690 --> 00:59.191
[crash]

01:04.397 --> 01:07.766
Oh. I usually get
letters by dragon.

01:07.768 --> 01:09.501
It IS the fastest
way to get mail.

01:13.807 --> 01:16.375
For me? Who would be
sending me a letter?

01:19.479 --> 01:22.481
It's the ponies
from my old village.

01:22.483 --> 01:23.582
Are they in danger?

01:23.584 --> 01:25.117
Are they upset with you?

01:25.119 --> 01:27.286
No. It's worse.

01:27.288 --> 01:30.122
They've invited me to the
annual sunset festival!

01:35.428 --> 01:38.797
<i>♪ My little pony,</i>
<i>my little pony ♪</i>

01:38.799 --> 01:40.732
<i>♪ Aaaahhh </i>

01:40.734 --> 01:42.801
<i>♪ My little Pony </i>

01:42.803 --> 01:45.370
<i>♪ I used to wonder what</i>
<i>friendship could be. ♪</i>

01:45.372 --> 01:47.272
<i>♪ My Little Pony </i>

01:47.274 --> 01:49.708
<i>♪ Until you all shared</i>
<i>its magic with me. ♪</i>

01:49.710 --> 01:51.743
<i>♪ Big adventure! </i>
<i>♪ Tons of fun </i>

01:51.745 --> 01:53.879
<i>♪ A beautiful heart!  </i>
<i>♪ Faithful and strong! </i>

01:53.881 --> 01:56.248
<i>♪ Sharing kindness </i>
<i>♪ it's an easy feat </i>

01:56.250 --> 01:58.250
<i>♪ And magic makes it</i>
<i>all complete! ♪</i>

01:58.252 --> 02:00.352
<i>♪ To have my little pony </i>

02:00.354 --> 02:03.689
<i>♪ Do you know you're all</i>
<i>my very best friends? ♪</i>

02:03.691 --> 02:05.858
♪

02:10.763 --> 02:17.336
♪

02:17.338 --> 02:18.303
[sigh]

02:23.910 --> 02:26.845
Uh, hey there,
everypony.

02:26.847 --> 02:31.583
Uh. Hey Starlight. What
are you doing here?

02:31.585 --> 02:36.155
I... I was invited. To
the Sunset Festival?

02:36.157 --> 02:39.725
Uh yeah. But we didn't think
you'd actually show up.

02:39.727 --> 02:42.794
You didn't think we really
wanted you here did you?

02:45.198 --> 02:49.568
But I apologized. I thought
everything was fine.

02:49.570 --> 02:51.637
[laughing]

02:57.243 --> 02:59.645
PLEASE. Stop. STOP!

02:59.647 --> 03:06.251
<i>♪ [eerie music] </i>

03:06.253 --> 03:09.855
What happened? Is
anypony there?

03:12.358 --> 03:16.195
Princess Luna? What
are you doing here?

03:16.197 --> 03:18.597
Dreams are my domain,
Starlight Glimmer.

03:18.599 --> 03:21.233
I am here because
you need me to be.

03:21.235 --> 03:24.369
Oh! It's only a dream.

03:24.371 --> 03:28.640
It may only be a dream, but
the feelings in it are real.

03:28.642 --> 03:30.976
Great. So I guess
I'm more afraid

03:30.978 --> 03:32.611
of going back
to the village

03:32.613 --> 03:35.347
than I thought.
What do I do now?

03:35.349 --> 03:36.949
I have been helped
time and time again

03:36.951 --> 03:39.618
by six very
special ponies.

03:39.620 --> 03:41.787
They helped me
overcome my past.

03:41.789 --> 03:44.423
You are fortunate to
have them as friends.

03:44.425 --> 03:46.825
I suggest you share your
concerns with them.

03:48.895 --> 03:51.630
I see much of myself in
you, Starlight Glimmer

03:51.632 --> 03:54.333
and I can tell you from
personal experience

03:54.335 --> 03:56.969
that things do
indeed get better.

03:56.971 --> 04:00.739
[whoosh]

04:00.741 --> 04:02.241
Huh?

04:05.545 --> 04:08.714
... and Princess Luna
said I should tell you all

04:08.716 --> 04:13.685
how I was feeling.
So, there it is.

04:13.687 --> 04:16.888
I'm afraid to go back to the
village for the celebration.

04:16.890 --> 04:20.892
But why, darling? You went back
to apologize; they accepted.

04:20.894 --> 04:23.328
Everypony has moved on!

04:23.330 --> 04:26.932
But have they? They don't really
know how much I've changed.

04:26.934 --> 04:29.468
Or even worse, maybe I
haven't changed as much

04:29.470 --> 04:31.470
as I think I have!

04:31.472 --> 04:35.007
TRUST ME. You are a totally
different pony now.

04:35.009 --> 04:37.309
I mean...you were
pretty awful!

04:37.311 --> 04:38.610
RAINBOW DASH!

04:38.612 --> 04:42.514
WHAT?! She WAS!
It's a compliment!

04:42.516 --> 04:44.583
I don't think they would
have sent the invitation

04:44.585 --> 04:46.418
if they didn't want
you to come.

04:46.420 --> 04:48.754
I'm sure they'd be
happy to see you.

04:48.756 --> 04:51.857
And getting an invitation
to a party and NOT GOING?

04:51.859 --> 04:54.660
That's like...
it's like...

04:54.662 --> 04:57.929
Well, I don't know what it's
like, but it is definitely bad.

04:57.931 --> 05:00.065
Just be honest
with them.

05:00.067 --> 05:02.567
I'm sure they'll understand
where you're comin' from.

05:02.569 --> 05:04.770
I understand how
hard this is for you.

05:04.772 --> 05:06.405
Maybe if you took
a friend along,

05:06.407 --> 05:07.739
it might
make things easier.

05:07.741 --> 05:10.676
Somepony you trust who
would look out for you.

05:16.816 --> 05:18.550
Thanks so much for
doing this, Trixie.

05:18.552 --> 05:20.319
When Twilight said I
should bring a friend,

05:20.321 --> 05:22.054
you were the first
pony I thought of.

05:22.056 --> 05:24.456
Great idea,
Princess Twilight.

05:24.458 --> 05:27.592
Asking me, Starlight's
BEST friend,

05:27.594 --> 05:29.861
to help her on this
difficult journey

05:29.863 --> 05:33.765
really shows how wise a
princess you have become.

05:33.767 --> 05:35.701
Thanks, Trixie.

05:35.703 --> 05:37.669
I was TALKING about me.

05:39.639 --> 05:41.006
The festival lasts
a whole week,

05:41.008 --> 05:43.008
but I'm sure we
won't stay that long.

05:43.010 --> 05:44.876
Oh I don't know,
Starlight,

05:44.878 --> 05:47.546
time really flies when
you're spending it

05:47.548 --> 05:49.614
with your BEST FRIEND!

05:55.888 --> 05:59.057
Bye Starlight!See
you later! Good luck!

06:03.763 --> 06:06.531
There it is! The
town where you --

06:06.533 --> 06:08.066
Magically stole
everypony's cutie mark,

06:08.068 --> 06:10.035
replaced them with equal
signs and forced them all

06:10.037 --> 06:13.138
to hide their
natural talents? Yes.

06:13.140 --> 06:16.775
I was going say
where you came from.

06:16.777 --> 06:20.779
But yours is a more...
emotionally traumatic answer.

06:20.781 --> 06:22.481
[sigh]

06:22.483 --> 06:25.517
I just want to blend in. Be
just another pony in the crowd

06:25.519 --> 06:27.819
enjoying the Sunset
Festival with my friend.

06:27.821 --> 06:30.489
Sounds good to me. And if
things get weird for you,

06:30.491 --> 06:32.924
just let me know.
I've got your flank.

06:32.926 --> 06:34.526
Is that a promise?

06:34.528 --> 06:39.798
Not just a promise. A GREAT
and POWERFUL promise.

06:39.800 --> 06:40.966
[pow!]

06:40.968 --> 06:43.402
[cough]

06:43.404 --> 06:46.171
Well, I couldn't ask
for more than that.

06:46.173 --> 06:48.540
If we're gonna do
this, let's do it!

06:58.184 --> 07:01.887
Ahh! STARLIGHT! YOU CAME!

07:01.889 --> 07:03.422
[nervous giggle]

07:03.424 --> 07:05.524
We were worried you
wouldn't be able to make it!

07:05.526 --> 07:06.825
Are you staying
the whole week?

07:06.827 --> 07:09.528
We have different
events planned each day!

07:09.530 --> 07:11.630
How is it living
in a castle?

07:11.632 --> 07:14.800
It is SO good
to see you.

07:14.802 --> 07:18.904
Oh yeah. These ponies
are terrifying.

07:18.906 --> 07:21.506
[giggle]

07:21.508 --> 07:24.209
It's good to see
all of you too.

07:24.211 --> 07:26.745
You got here
JUST in time.

07:26.747 --> 07:29.581
We were having some debate
about these banners.

07:29.583 --> 07:33.018
Which do you think
feels more sunsety?

07:33.020 --> 07:36.054
Oh, you don't need
me to decide that.

07:36.056 --> 07:38.623
Whatever you think
is probably best.

07:38.625 --> 07:40.992
Uh well, how about
helping us with the routes

07:40.994 --> 07:44.463
for the relay races tomorrow.
Can you take a look?

07:44.465 --> 07:47.666
Oh, I shouldn't.
You all go ahead.

07:47.668 --> 07:49.801
I just want to
enjoy the festival.

07:49.803 --> 07:52.938
But you WILL be a judge for
the baking competition, right?

07:52.940 --> 07:55.207
We had a few questions
about the order of the acts

07:55.209 --> 07:57.042
for the talent show.

07:57.044 --> 07:59.478
And the unicorns have a
fireworks show planned.

07:59.480 --> 08:01.213
We could REALLY
use your help!

08:01.215 --> 08:03.482
[Talking over each other]

08:08.921 --> 08:09.921
NO!

08:09.923 --> 08:10.922
[explosion]

08:10.924 --> 08:13.191
[chattering teeth]

08:13.193 --> 08:17.195
Huh?

08:17.197 --> 08:20.632
The great and powerful Trixie
would like to thank you all

08:20.634 --> 08:22.601
for being such an
amazing audience!

08:22.603 --> 08:24.703
Sadly it is time
for us to depart!

08:24.705 --> 08:26.905
Good night, fillies
and gentlefoals!

08:26.907 --> 08:27.806
[explosion]

08:27.808 --> 08:30.575
[coughing]

08:30.577 --> 08:33.879
[all chattering]

08:41.554 --> 08:44.890
Ugh. I was horrible
when I led that town.

08:44.892 --> 08:47.959
I was ready for them to not
trust me, but I wasn't ready

08:47.961 --> 08:50.762
for them to put me
in charge again!

08:50.764 --> 08:54.065
With my past, I should never
be in charge of anything.

08:54.067 --> 08:56.801
So you messed
up. Big deal.

08:58.638 --> 09:01.806
Don't you ever tell
another pony I said this,

09:01.808 --> 09:05.877
but even Trixie's made
mistakes. Ha, I know!

09:05.879 --> 09:10.115
The trick is to just move on and
pretend they never happened!

09:10.117 --> 09:12.817
I feel like that's
almost good advice.

09:19.091 --> 09:22.127
Hey! Uh, Pinkie Pie!

09:22.129 --> 09:24.696
Hey, you!

09:24.698 --> 09:28.166
So. You're probably wondering
why I'm back so soon.

09:28.168 --> 09:29.901
Where were you?

09:29.903 --> 09:33.572
I went to my old village?
For the festival?

09:33.574 --> 09:36.875
Ooo sounds fun!
How was it!

09:36.877 --> 09:38.743
It was kind of a disaster.

09:38.745 --> 09:40.946
I came back early
because I freaked out.

09:40.948 --> 09:43.014
Oooh, sounds awful! Bye!

09:45.818 --> 09:48.253
That was strange.

09:48.255 --> 09:50.689
Isn't she always strange?

09:50.691 --> 09:52.924
Yeah, but not like that.

09:52.926 --> 09:55.827
Hey! I'm back early!

09:55.829 --> 09:58.330
Ah, welcome
back.

09:58.332 --> 10:01.232
Have you two noticed Pinkie
acting a little strange?

10:01.234 --> 10:03.134
Pinkie Pie always
acts strange.

10:04.203 --> 10:05.870
Told you.

10:05.872 --> 10:08.073
Anyway, I wanted to
talk to all of you.

10:08.075 --> 10:10.709
Things didn't go the way I
thought they were going to go

10:10.711 --> 10:11.943
at the Sunset Festival.

10:11.945 --> 10:13.345
What happened?

10:13.347 --> 10:16.381
I kind of freaked out and
ran out of the village.

10:16.383 --> 10:18.984
HA HA HA!

10:18.986 --> 10:21.853
You freaked out and ran
away from a festival?

10:21.855 --> 10:25.957
Ha! That's the funniest dang
thing I've heard all day!

10:25.959 --> 10:29.894
Ha ha, Oh my! Let me guess. The
decorations were TERRIFYING!

10:29.896 --> 10:36.234
HA HA HA!

10:36.236 --> 10:39.237
[Whisper]

10:39.239 --> 10:42.874
Hello ponies. We need
Rarity and Applejack.

10:42.876 --> 10:45.644
Very important
friendship business.

10:51.017 --> 10:54.085
I have to say I'm really not
as impressed with your friends

10:54.087 --> 10:56.655
as the rest of
Equestria is.

10:56.657 --> 10:58.289
I need to talk
to Twilight.

10:58.291 --> 11:04.162
♪

11:04.164 --> 11:05.296
[knock on door]

11:05.298 --> 11:08.333
Twilight! Hello?

11:08.335 --> 11:11.102
What do you want?
Twilight's very busy!

11:11.104 --> 11:13.304
Spike, I really need
to speak with her.

11:13.306 --> 11:18.276
Make an appointment! She's
a princess after all. [slam]

11:18.278 --> 11:21.012
[knocking] What's wrong with
you? Why are you being so--

11:21.014 --> 11:25.350
Rude? I think a certain dragon
didn't get his nap today!

11:25.352 --> 11:28.086
Yeah right. Whatever...

11:28.088 --> 11:31.056
Sorry, he's been acting
a little off all day.

11:31.058 --> 11:32.957
I think he missed a
meal or something.

11:32.959 --> 11:34.426
He's not the
only one.

11:34.428 --> 11:37.829
Everypony is acting a
little strange today.

11:37.831 --> 11:42.300
Yes. It's definitely been one
of those days. How are you?

11:42.302 --> 11:44.703
Not great actually.
You're probably wondering

11:44.705 --> 11:47.172
why I'm back from the
village so early.

11:47.174 --> 11:50.775
I didn't want to bring it up but
yeah, it did seem strange.

11:50.777 --> 11:52.243
Did it not go well?

11:52.245 --> 11:54.245
The townsponies kept
asking me things,

11:54.247 --> 11:56.881
like they expected me
to be in charge again.

11:56.883 --> 11:59.884
But being a leader is the
last thing I should ever be.

11:59.886 --> 12:04.489
So we left. Very suddenly.
In a literal puff of smoke.

12:04.491 --> 12:08.760
Wow. You should DEFINITELY
never go back to that village!

12:08.762 --> 12:10.195
What?

12:10.197 --> 12:13.131
If you were worried about what
they thought of you before,

12:13.133 --> 12:17.068
it's probably WAY worse
now. I'd cut my losses.

12:17.070 --> 12:20.739
That's surprising
advice coming from you.

12:20.741 --> 12:23.808
Trust me. I'm the
Princess of Friendship.

12:23.810 --> 12:27.011
You don't need those ponies. You
can always make more friends.

12:29.882 --> 12:32.250
Ah, speaking of friends,
if you'll excuse me.

12:32.252 --> 12:33.785
Important business to attend to!

12:38.924 --> 12:40.291
[slam]

12:40.293 --> 12:43.361
♪ [mysterious music]

12:47.833 --> 12:51.202
Cut my losses? That
can't be right.

12:51.204 --> 12:54.272
♪

13:06.385 --> 13:11.156
Hey! I wanted to apologize
for my behavior earlier.

13:11.158 --> 13:15.827
Party Favor? Can you hear me?

13:15.829 --> 13:20.932
I TOLD you, you can never
speak to them again!

13:20.934 --> 13:22.901
What are you all doing here?

13:22.903 --> 13:27.338
Making sure you do what I said!
I'm your teacher,aren't I?

13:27.340 --> 13:29.941
Didn't I say to
never come back here?

13:29.943 --> 13:32.510
Yes, but that's just
doesn't seem right.

13:32.512 --> 13:37.115
You aren't acting like
yourself. Something is wrong.

13:37.117 --> 13:39.818
[whistling wind]

13:39.820 --> 13:42.587
A dream! This is
another dream!

13:42.589 --> 13:44.155
<i>Starlight Glimmer...</i>

13:44.157 --> 13:45.890
Princess Luna?

13:45.892 --> 13:47.358
<i>Starlight Glimmer!</i>

13:47.360 --> 13:49.427
Princess Luna, where are you?

13:49.429 --> 13:52.831
STARLIGHT GLIMMER!THERE IS
NO TIME! YOU MUST GET HELP!

13:52.833 --> 13:55.834
What? What are you talking
about? This is just a dream!

13:55.836 --> 13:59.470
NOT HERE! IN THE WAKING WORLD!
THEY'VE TAKEN MY SISTER AND I!

13:59.472 --> 14:01.306
IT'S WORSE THAN THE LAST TIME!

14:01.308 --> 14:03.842
YOUR DREAM CALLED TO ME AND
I WAS ABLE TO BREAK THROUGH!

14:03.844 --> 14:05.109
YOU MUST FIND HELP!

14:05.111 --> 14:07.111
What are you saying?
WHO'S taken you!

14:07.113 --> 14:09.314
BE CAREFUL WHO YOU TRUST.

14:09.316 --> 14:11.382
YOU WILL NEED ALL THE
HELP YOU CAN FIND.

14:11.384 --> 14:12.450
THE CHANGELINGS
HAVE RETURNED AND--

14:12.452 --> 14:15.620
Princess Luna!

14:15.622 --> 14:18.923
[whoosh]

14:18.925 --> 14:20.358
[gasping]

14:20.360 --> 14:21.559
THEY'RE BACK!

14:33.939 --> 14:35.173
[knocking]

14:35.175 --> 14:38.509
Trixie? Trixie, it's
Starlight! Are you awake?

14:38.511 --> 14:42.447
Of COURSE Princess Celestia,
I'd love to perform

14:42.449 --> 14:44.482
for Peanut Butter crackers.

14:44.484 --> 14:46.217
TRIXIE! WAKE UP!

14:48.587 --> 14:53.024
[firecrackers explosions
and whistles]

14:53.026 --> 14:57.362
[coughing]

14:57.364 --> 15:01.933
Starlight? What time is it?

15:01.935 --> 15:05.036
It's late. I think I figured out
what's wrong with my friends.

15:05.038 --> 15:06.638
I have a whole
list of things

15:06.640 --> 15:08.473
that are wrong
with your friends.

15:08.475 --> 15:11.109
We can go over it
in the morning.

15:11.111 --> 15:13.278
No! Trixie, we're in danger!

15:16.282 --> 15:21.019
OK fine. Aside from lack of
sleep, how are we in danger?

15:21.021 --> 15:23.421
I think the--

15:23.423 --> 15:27.325
What did you tell me never
to tell another pony?

15:27.327 --> 15:30.595
Starlight, if you woke me
up to play guessing games--

15:30.597 --> 15:32.330
After we left my village!

15:32.332 --> 15:37.402
What did you tell me to never
tell another pony you said!?

15:37.404 --> 15:40.271
That even Trixie's
made mistakes.

15:40.273 --> 15:43.608
Trixie, there's no time for
this. What did you say?

15:43.610 --> 15:48.579
That even Trixie's made
mistakes, OK? Are you happy?

15:48.581 --> 15:53.051
Yes. Sorry. I just had to make
sure you weren't one of them.

15:53.053 --> 15:54.085
One of who?

15:54.087 --> 15:55.954
A changeling.

15:55.956 --> 15:58.556
I think they've taken Princess
Celestia and Princess Luna.

15:58.558 --> 16:01.392
What? Are you sure? I
mean, what do we--

16:01.394 --> 16:03.361
We have to tell Twilight!

16:03.363 --> 16:06.230
If I'm right, then it's
too late for that.

16:17.242 --> 16:22.146
[muffled conversation]

16:26.752 --> 16:28.019
Agh!

16:28.420 --> 16:29.520
Agh!

16:29.522 --> 16:32.090
[nasty laugh]

16:34.193 --> 16:35.493
Is it ready?

16:35.495 --> 16:37.395
Just one more.

16:38.497 --> 16:40.565
[zapping]

16:46.005 --> 16:48.439
QUEEN CHRYSALIS!

16:48.441 --> 16:51.309
Ugh, I can't take
any of you seriously

16:51.311 --> 16:52.677
when you look like that.

16:52.679 --> 16:54.145
Oh. Right.

17:01.153 --> 17:04.255
MUCH better. Now report.

17:04.257 --> 17:07.025
Everything here is going
according to plan.

17:07.027 --> 17:09.527
We've replaced the six
ponies and their dragon

17:09.529 --> 17:12.397
and have taken
control of the castle.

17:12.399 --> 17:15.433
Excellent. And I've
just received word

17:15.435 --> 17:17.702
that the Princesses from
Canterlot have successfully

17:17.704 --> 17:19.771
been replaced as well.

17:19.773 --> 17:23.107
[cackling]

17:23.109 --> 17:25.476
We thought too small last time,

17:25.478 --> 17:28.579
ONE ponynapped
princess wasn't enough.

17:28.581 --> 17:32.316
With ALL the most beloved ponies
of Equestria taken care of,

17:32.318 --> 17:34.819
NOPONY can stop us.

17:34.821 --> 17:39.724
[evil laugh]

17:39.726 --> 17:41.059
[whoosh]

17:42.461 --> 17:43.461
[creak]

17:43.463 --> 17:45.296
[hiss]

17:45.298 --> 17:47.065
[whoosh]

17:59.545 --> 18:03.815
[sniff sniff]

18:11.190 --> 18:13.257
[panicked whimpering]

18:13.259 --> 18:15.493
[zap zap]

18:15.495 --> 18:18.729
I can't deal with this.
I'm just a performer.

18:18.731 --> 18:21.532
This is... this is
princess level stuff.

18:21.534 --> 18:25.570
But the changeling's have all of
the princesses. We're doomed!

18:25.572 --> 18:29.474
Maybe not. Queen Chrysalis only
said they took Luna and Celestia

18:29.476 --> 18:31.309
and obviously Twilight
and the others,

18:31.311 --> 18:33.277
but maybe Cadance is still safe.

18:33.279 --> 18:35.446
Our best bet is to get
to the Crystal Empire

18:35.448 --> 18:37.381
before the changelings
do. That way we--

18:37.383 --> 18:39.684
<i>There's no help coming</i>
<i>from the Crystal Empire.</i>

18:41.887 --> 18:45.690
[frantic screaming]

18:45.692 --> 18:46.724
Thorax?

18:46.726 --> 18:47.692
Yes.

18:47.694 --> 18:49.527
Your wings look... different.

18:51.530 --> 18:53.264
I guess they do.

18:56.335 --> 18:58.436
How do I know you aren't
some other changeling

18:58.438 --> 19:01.139
pretending to be Throax?

19:01.141 --> 19:03.508
You were there when Spike
defended me to the ponies

19:03.510 --> 19:05.276
of the Crystal Empire.

19:05.278 --> 19:07.745
Princess Twilight said...

19:07.747 --> 19:11.149
As the Princess of Friendship,
I should set an example

19:11.151 --> 19:15.319
for all of Equestria, but today,
it was Spike who taught me--

19:15.321 --> 19:18.789
OK! OK. I believe you. We
don't need the whole speech.

19:21.193 --> 19:23.594
Trixie, this is Thorax.

19:23.596 --> 19:27.365
He's a reformed changeling.
He's on our side, understand?

19:29.868 --> 19:32.436
Hi, it's a pleasure to--

19:32.438 --> 19:35.406
If Starlight says you're on
our side I believe her but...

19:35.408 --> 19:37.875
maybe just stay over
there for now, OK?

19:39.778 --> 19:41.612
What did you mean
there's no help.

19:41.614 --> 19:44.515
Did the changelings
get Cadance too?

19:44.517 --> 19:48.319
They took Cadance, Shining
Armor AND Flurry Heart!

19:48.321 --> 19:50.821
Sunburst sent me here to get
Princess Twilight's help

19:50.823 --> 19:54.292
but it sounds like it's
too late for that too.

19:54.294 --> 19:56.294
So what should we do?

19:56.296 --> 19:59.397
Yeah, Starlight what
are we going to do?

19:59.399 --> 20:02.833
I... I don't know. There
has to be somepony else

20:02.835 --> 20:04.368
who can handle this.

20:04.370 --> 20:06.537
There is NOPONY else.

20:06.539 --> 20:09.807
Everypony with powerful
magic is already gone!

20:09.809 --> 20:12.343
You know, whenever ponies
talk about powerful magic,

20:12.345 --> 20:14.212
they always leave me out.

20:14.214 --> 20:17.815
If I weren't so evolved, I might
decide to take it personally.

20:17.817 --> 20:19.650
Well, isn't this
QUITE the combination

20:19.652 --> 20:22.386
of secondary characters.

20:22.388 --> 20:24.422
Where are Twilight
and the girls?

20:24.424 --> 20:27.825
First, how do we know
that you're really you?

20:28.627 --> 20:29.860
[snap]

20:29.862 --> 20:35.433
♪

20:35.435 --> 20:37.401
Shall I continue?

20:37.403 --> 20:39.503
Chrysalis and the
changelings are back.

20:39.505 --> 20:41.372
They've ponynapped all of
the most powerful ponies

20:41.374 --> 20:42.840
in Equestria.

20:42.842 --> 20:45.843
Celestia, Luna, Cadance,
Shining Armor, Flurry Heart,

20:45.845 --> 20:48.479
Twilight and her
friends. We need to--

20:48.481 --> 20:49.880
They took Fluttershy?

20:49.882 --> 20:50.915
Yes.

20:50.917 --> 20:52.650
Where?

20:52.652 --> 20:55.019
The changeling kingdom. With
you on our side, I think we --

20:55.021 --> 20:56.287
[poof]

20:57.789 --> 21:01.525
Odd. I was trying to take
us right to Fluttershy,

21:01.527 --> 21:04.295
but there is no Fluttershy.

21:04.997 --> 21:07.331
[smash]

21:07.333 --> 21:10.801
I think I have a pretty good
idea where she might be.

21:10.803 --> 21:13.871
♪ [dramatic]

21:18.377 --> 21:22.713
Oh. I'd hoped to never see
that place again. Now what?

21:22.715 --> 21:25.783
♪

21:31.957 --> 21:34.358
<i>♪ My Little Pony </i>

21:36.361 --> 21:38.529
<i>♪ My Little Pony </i>

21:49.441 --> 21:51.509
<i>♪ My Little Pony </i>

21:51.511 --> 21:55.313
<i>♪ friends </i>
